<title>ạ̹lhy ạ̹lhy kn qạỷdy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ạ̹lhy ạ̹lhy kn qạỷdy .. fy msyrẗ ạlṣlb lạ̉qtdy)2
 (ạ̉rạk ḍʿyfaⁿạ wạ̉nt ạlqwy .. tṣfḥ wtgẖfr lkl mʿtdy)2
 ạlqrạr- (ạ̹fʿl by mạ tryd .. ạ̉nt rfyqy ạlwḥyd)2
 (qd ṣrt mljạ̉y fy kl ḍyq .. ạ̉srʿ ạ̹lyk wạ̉ḥtmy fyk)2
 2- (hạ ṣlyb ạlʿạr qd ḥmlth .. bkl fkẖạriⁿ qd rfʿth)2
 (ạ̹ly̱ ạljljtẖẗ ḥytẖ wḍʿth .. ʿly̱ rbwẗiⁿ ʿạlyẗ tẖbth)2
 3- (qd wḍʿt dẖạtk ʿly̱ ṣlyb ạlʿạr .. mstslmaⁿạ lh bkl ạ̹ṣrạr)2
 (ạ̉smʿ dqẗ qlbk mʿ dqẗ ạlmsmạr .. tʿln lyã ḥbk yạ qdws yạ bạr)2
 4- (yạ lh mn ʿml sry ạ̹lhy ʿjyb .. ạ̉ṣyr sẖrykaⁿạ fy ṭbyʿẗ ạlḥbyb)2
 (hmsạt ḥbh llqlb tdẖyb .. ṣrt lh ạ̉syraⁿạ wạ̉kẖdẖth lyã nṣyb)2</lyrics>
</song>